@host = https://localhost:7155
@scheduleId = 11111111-2222-3333-4444-555555555555

### Get All Schedules
GET {{host}}/api/production

### Create Schedule
POST {{host}}/api/production
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Sourdough Bread",
  "quantity": 20,
  "scheduledTime": "2026-05-10T08:00:00Z"
}

### Get Schedule By Id
GET {{host}}/api/production/{{scheduleId}}

### Start Baking
POST {{host}}/api/production/{{scheduleId}}/start

### Complete Baking
POST {{host}}/api/production/{{scheduleId}}/complete

### Get Non-existent Schedule
GET {{host}}/api/production/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
# Expected: 404 Not Found
